<h2>rwlock</h2>
    <p>This attribute can only be used to modify class and category, which means class object generated by this class or category can use the reader writer lock mechanism. For example: </p>
    <pre class="code">
component Demo
{
    бнбн
    [uuid(e2e599e2-fe49-4010-ba97-cd644719747c), <b>rwlock</b>]
    class CDemo {
        бнбн
    }
}
</pre>
    <p></p>
    <p>If the component uses this attribute, the client program can invoke <a class="style1" href="../inline_func/MyCReaderWriterLockPart.htm">MyCReaderWriterLockPart</a> method to obtain the class smart pointer <a class="style1" href="../../../zee/class/CReaderWriterLockRef.htm">CReaderWriterLockRef</a> and use all methods in class <a class="style1" href="../../../zee/class/CReaderWriterLock.htm">CReaderWriterLock</a>.</p>
    <p>This attribute can be used with other attributes.</p>
